### ========== 错误场景测试 ==========

### 测试：手机号已注册
POST http://localhost:8080/user/sendVerifyCode
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138000"
}

### 预期响应：{"code":500,"msg":"该手机号已注册"}

###

### 测试：验证码错误
POST http://localhost:8080/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13700137003",
  "password": "123456",
  "verifyCode": "000000",
  "breedingType": "养猪",
  "position": "老板"
}

### 预期响应：{"code":500,"msg":"验证码错误或已过期"}

###

### 测试：参数验证 - 手机号为空
POST http://localhost:8080/user/sendVerifyCode
